hadiths[87]{hadithnumber,text}:
6621,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) kabhi apni qism nahi todtey they, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne qism ka kaffara utaaraa. us waqt unhon-ne kaha ke ab agar main koi qism khaaunga aur uske siwa koi cheez bhalai ki hogi to main wahi kaam karunga jis mein bhalai ho aur apni qism ka kaffara de doonga ."
6622,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abdur-Rehman bin Samra ! kabhi kisi hukumat ke ohda ki darkhaast na karna kyonke agar tumhen ye maangney ke baad milega to Allah paak apni madad tujh se utha lega, to jaan , tera kaam janey aur agar wo ohda tumhen baghair maangey mil gaya to usmein Allah ki taraf se tumhari iaa'nat ki jaeygi aur jab tum koi qism kha lo aur uske siwa kisi aur cheez mein bhalai dekho to apni qism ka kaffara de do aur wo kaam karo jo bhalai ka ho."
6623,"mein Ash-ari qabeele ki aik jamat ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se sawari mangi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism , main tumharey liye sawari ka koi intizam nahi kar sakta aur na mere paas koi sawari ka janwar hai. bayan kya phir jitney dinon Allah ne chaha ham yoonhii thahrey rahe. iske baad teen achi qism ki oontniyan laai gain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hamein sawari ke liye inayat farmaya, jab ham rawaana huey to ham ne kaha ya ham mein se kuchh ne kaha, Allah ki qism ! hamein usmein barkat nahi hasil hogi. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sawari maangney aaey they, to aap ne qism kha li thi ke aap hamarey liye sawari ka intizam nahi kar saktey aur ab aap ne hamein sawari inayat farmai hai hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jana chahiye aur aapko qism yad dilaanii chahiye chunanche ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhari sawari ka koi intizam nahi kya hai balke Allah Taala ne ye intizam kya hai aur main, Allah ki qasam! koi bhi qism agar kha loonga aur uske siwa kisi aur cheez mein bhalai dekhoonga to apni qism ka kaffara de doonga. jis mein bhalai hogi ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke wahi karunga jis mein bhalai hogi aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar doonga."
6624,ye wo hadis hai jo ham se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ''ham aakhiri ummat hain aur qiyamat ke din jannat mein sabse pahley dakhil hongey. ''
6625,phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism ( kabhi-kabhi ( apne ghar walon ke maamle main tumhara apni qasmon par israar kartey rehna Allah ke nazdeek us se zyada gunah ki baat hoti hai ke) qism tod kar) uska wo kaffara ada kar diya jaey jo Allah Taala ne is par farz kya hai.
6626,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''wo shakhs jo apne ghar walon ke maamle mein qism par ada rehta hai wo us se bada gunah karta hai ke is qism ka kaffara ada kar de. ''
6627,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik fauj bheji aur uska ameer Usama-bin-Zaid ko banaya. kuchh logon ne unke ameer banaey janey par aetraz kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya ke agar tum log iske ameer banaey janey par aetraz kartey ho to tum us se pahley iske walid Zaid ke ameer banaey janey par bhi aetraz kar chukey ho aur Allah ki qism ! Zaid ameer banaey janey ke qaabil they aur mujhey sab logon se zyada azeez they aur ye ( Usama ( unke baad mujhey sabse zyada azeez they.
6628,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qism bas itni thi ke nahi ! dilon ke pherney waley Allah ki qism .
6629,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab qaisar halaak ho jaeyga to phir uske baad koi qaisar nahi paida hoga aur jab Kisraa halaak ho jaeyga to iske baad koi Kisraa nahi paida hoga aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai tum unke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein kharch karogey.''
6630,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Kisraa ( badshah Iraan ( halaak ho jaeyga to iske baad koi Kisraa nahi paida hoga aur jab qaisar ( badshah Rome (mojooda Itly) ( halaak ho jaeyga to iske baad koi qaisar nahi paida hoga aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai tum unke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein kharch karogey. ''
6631,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey ummate-Muhammad ! Allah ki qism , agar tum wo jantey jo main janta hun to zyada rotey aur kam hanstey.''"
6632,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they aur aap umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath pakdey huey they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap mujhey har cheez se zyada azeez hain, siwa meri apni jaan ke. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. (eman us waqt tak mukammal nahi ho sakta ( jab tak main tumhen tumhari apni jaan se bhi zyada azeez na ho jaun. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : phir Allah ki qism ! ab aap mujhey meri apni jaan se bhi zyada azeez hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, umr ! ab tera eman pura hua."
6633,"2 aadmiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein apna jhagdaa pesh kya. unmein se aik ne kaha ke hamarey darmyan aap kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. doosrey ne, jo zyada samajhdaar tha kaha ke theek hai, ya Rasulullah! hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dijiye aur mujhey ijazat dijiye ke us maamle mein kuchh arz karun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho. un sahib ne kaha ke mera ladka us shakhs ke yahan ( Aseef ( tha. ( Aseef ( , Mina ( الأجير ( ko kehtey hain. ( الأجير (ke mana mazdoor ke hain) aur us ne uski biwi se zina kar liya. unhon-ne mujh se kaha ke ab mere ladkey ko sangsaar kya jaeyga isliye (is se nijat dilaane ke liye) maine so bakriyon aur aik londi ka unhein fidya de diya phir maine doosrey ilm walon se us masla ko puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ki saza ye hai ke usey so kode lagaey jayen aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kar diya jaey, sangsaari ki saza sirf us aurat ko hogi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga . tumhari bakriyan aur tumhari londi tumhen wapas hogi aur phir aap ne iske ladkey ko so kode lagwaaey aur aik saal ke liye jilaa watan kar diya. phir aap ne Anees Aslami se farmaya ke muddaii ki biwi ko laey aur agar wo zina ka iqrar karey to usey sangsaar kar de. us aurat ne zina ka iqrar kar liya aur sangsaar kar di gaee."
6634,"2 aadmiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein apna jhagdaa pesh kya. unmein se aik ne kaha ke hamarey darmyan aap kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dein. doosrey ne, jo zyada samajh daar tha kaha ke theek hai, ya Rasulullah ! hamarey darmyan kitabullah ke mutabiq faisla kar dijiye aur mujhey ijazat dijiye ke is maamle mein kuchh arz karun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kaho. un sahib ne kaha ke mera ladka is shakhs ke yahan ( Aseef ( tha. ( Aseef ), Mina ( الأجير ( ko kehtey hain. ( الأجير (ke mana mazdoor ke hain) aur us ne uski biwi se zina kar liya. unhon-ne mujh se kaha ke ab mere ladkey ko sangsaar kya jaeyga isliye (is se nijat dilaane ke liye) maine so bakriyon aur aik londi ka unhein fidya de diya phir maine doosrey ilm walon se is mas'ale ko puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke mere ladkey ki saza ye hai ke usey so kode lagaey jayen aur aik saal ke liye Shahar badr kar diya jaey, sangsaari ki saza sirf us aurat ko hogi. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main tumhara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq karunga . tumhari bakriyan aur tumhari londi tumhen wapas hogi aur phir aap ne iske ladkey ko so kode lagwaaey aur aik saal ke liye jalaa watan kar diya. phir aap ne Anees Aslami se farmaya ke muddaii ki biwi ko laey aur agar wo zina ka iqrar karey to usey sangsaar kar de. us aurat ne zina ka iqrar kar liya aur sangsaar kar di gaee."
6635,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' bhala batlao Aslam, ghifaar, muzena aur juhaina ke qabeeley agar Tameem, Aamir bin sa'sa'a, Ghatfan aur Asad walon se behtar hon to ye Tameem aur Aamir aur Ghatfan aur Asad waley ghaatey mein padey aur nuqsan mein rahe ya nahi. sahaba ne arz kya : ji haan beshak. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par phir farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai (wo pahley jin qabaayel ka zikr hua) un (Tameem wghaira) se behtar hain."
6636,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aamil (governor) muqarrar kya. aamil apne kaam poorey karke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye maal aap ka hai aur ye maal mujhey tohfa diya gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum apne maan-baap ke ghar hi mein kyon nahi baithey rahe aur phir dekhtey ke tumhen koi tohfa deta hai ya nahi. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutbe ke liye khadey huey, raat ki Namaz ke baad aur kalima shahadat aur Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq sana ke baad farmaya ammaa ba'd! aisey aamil ko kya ho gaya hai ke ham usey aamil banatey hain. ( jiziya aur doosrey tax wsool karne ke liye) aur wo phir hamarey paas aa kar kehta hai ke ye to aap ka tax hai aur mujhey tohfa diya gaya hai. phir wo apne maan-baap ke ghar kyon nahi betha aur dekhta ke usey tohfa diya jata hai ya nahi. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, agar tum mein se koi bhi us maal mein se kuchh bhi khayanat karega to qiyamat ke din usey apni gardan par uthaaeyga. agar oont ki us ne khayanat ki hogi to us haal mein lekar aayega ke awaz nikal rahi hogi. agar gaaey ki khayanat ki hogi to us haal mein usey lekar aayega ke gaaey ki awaz aa rahi hogi. agar bakri ki khayanat ki hogi to us haal mein aayega ke bakri ki awaz aa rahi hogi. bas maine tum tak pahuncha diya. abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath itni uper uthaya ke ham aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhney lagey. abu-Humed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mere sath ye hadis Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi, tum log unse bhi poochh lo."
6637,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism ! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar tum bhi aakhirat ki wo mushkilaat jantey jo main janta hun to tum zyada rotey aur kam hanstey.''
6638,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahuncha to aap Kaba ke saaye mein baithey huey farma rahe they Kaba ke rab ki qism ! wahi sabse zyada khasaarey waley hain. Kaba ke rab ki qism ! wahi sabse zyada khasaarey waley hain. maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! meri haalat kaisi hai, kya mujh main ( bhi) koi aisi baat nazar aai hai? meri haalat kaisi hai? phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baith gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ja rahe they, mein aapko khamosh nahi kara sakta tha aur Allah ki marzi ke mutabiq mujh par ajeeb be-qaraarii taarii ho gaee. maine phir arz ki, mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon, ya Rasulullah ! wo kon log hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye wo log hain jinke paas maal zyada hai. lekin us se wo mustashnaa hain. jinhoney usmein se is-is tarah (yani daaein aur baaein be-daregh mustahiqeen par) Allah ki raah mein kharch kya hoga."
6639,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne aik din kaha ke aaj main raat main apni nawwey beeviyon ke paas jaaunga aur har aik ke yahan aik ghud-sawaar bachcha paida hoga jo Allah ke raaste mein jihad karega . is par unke sathi ne kaha ke inshaAllah . lekin Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne inshaAllah nahi kaha, chunanche wo apni tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey lekin aik aurat ke siwa kisi ko hamal nahi hua aur us se bhi naaqis bachcha paida hua aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! agar unhon-ne inshaAllah keh diya hota to ( tamam beeviyon ke yahan bachchey paida hotey (aur sab ghodon par Sawar ho kar Allah ke rastey mein jihad karne waley hotey .''"
6640,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein resham ka aik tukda hadiya ke taur par aaya to log usey dast badast apne hathon mein leney lagey aur uski khoobsoortii aur narmii par hairat karne lagey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tumhen is par hairat hai? sahaba ne kaha ji haan , ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke roomaal jannat mein us se bhi achchhey hain. Shoba aur Israel ne Abu-Ishaq se alfaz ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai'' ka zikr nahi kya."
6641,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Hind binte- Utba-bin- Rabee (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki maan ( ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! saari zameen par jitney derney waley hain (yani Arab log jo aksar deron aur khemon mein raha kartey they) mein kisi ka zaleel w khuwaar hona mujh ko itna pasand nahi tha jitna aap kaa. Yahya-bin-Bukair rawi ko shak hai ab koi dere wala ya derey waley unko izzat aur aabroo hasil hona mujh ko aap ke derney walon se zyada pasand nahi hai (yani ab main aap ki aur musalmanon ki sabse zyada khair-khaah hun) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke abhi kya hai to aur bhi zyada khair-khaah banegii. qism hai uski jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai. phir Hind kehney lagi ya Rasulullah! Abu-Sufiyan to aik kanjoos aadmi hai mujh par gunah to nahi hoga agar main iske maal mein se (apne baal bachchon ko khilaaun) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi agar to dastoor ke muwafiq kharch kare.
6642,"aik mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab yamnii chamdey ke kheme se pusht lagaey huey baithey they, to aap ne apne sahaba se farmaya kya tum is par khush ho ke tum ahle-jannat ke aik chothai raho? unhon-ne arz kya, kyon nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke tum ahle-jannat ke aik tehai hissey paogey sahaba ne arz kya kyon nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya, to us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey ummeed hai ke jannat mein aadhey tum hi hogey."
6643,"aik sahabi ne suna ke aik doosrey sahabi sura ikhlas baar-baar padhtey hain jab subah hui to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya, wo sahabi is sura ko kam samajhtey they lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ye Quran Majeed ke aik tehai hisse ke barabar hai."
6644,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim kareem (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke rukoo aur sajda poorey taur par ada kya karo. Allah ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai main apni kamar ke peechhey se tum ko dekh leta hun jab rukoo aur sajda kartey ho."
6645,"Ansari khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin, unke sath unke bachchey bhi they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai tum log bhi mujhey tamam logon mein sabse zyada azeez ho. ye alfaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba farmaaey."
6646,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey to wo sawaaron ki aik jamat ke sath chal rahe they aur apne bap ki qism kha rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khabardaar tahqeeq Allah Taala ne tumhen bap daadon ki qism khaney se mana kya hai, jisey qism khaani hai usey chahiye ke Allah hi ki qism khaaey warna chup rahe."
6647,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke Allah Taala ne tumhen bap daadon ki qism khaney se mana kya hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya Allah ki qism ! phir maine unki Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se manaahii sunney ke baad kabhi qism nahi khaaii na apni taraf se ghairullaah ki qism khaaii na kisi doosrey ki zaban se naql ki. Mujahid ne kaha sura ehqaaf mein jo أثرة من علم hai iska mana ye hai ke ilm ki koi baat naql karta ho. Yunus ke sath us hadis ko Aqeel aur Muhammad-bin Waleed Zubaidi aur Ishaq bin Yahya kalbi ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Mamar ne usko Zohri se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke aap ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghairullaah ki qism khaatey suna. riwayat mein lafz ( اثارة ( ki tafseer ( اثرا ( ki munaasibat se bayan kar di kyonke donon ka maadda (route) aik hi hai."
6648,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' apne bap daadon ki qism na khaao .''
6649,"qabila jurm aur ash'ar ke darmyan bhai chaara tha. ham abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood they, to unke liye khana laya gaya. usmein murghi bhi thi. unke paas bani taimillaah ka aik surkh rang ka aadmi bhi maujood tha. ghaaliban wo ghulaamon mein se tha. abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey khaney par bulaya to usne kaha ke maine murghi ko gandagi khaatey dekha to mujhey ghin aai aur phir maine qism kha li ke ab main iska gosht nahi khaaunga. abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke khadey ho jao to main tumhen iske barey mein aik hadis sunaun . main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas qabila ash'ar ke chand logon ke sath aaya aur ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawari ka janwar maanga . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism main tumhen sawari nahi de sakta aur na mere paas aisa koi janwar hai jo tumhen sawari ke liye de sakoon, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh maale-ghanimat ke oont aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke Ash-ari log kahan hain phir aap ne ham ko panch umda qism ke oont diye janey ka hukm farmaya, jab ham unko lekar chaley to ham ne kaha ye ham ne kya kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to qism kha chukey they ke ham ko sawari nahi dengey aur dar-haqiqat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas us waqt sawari maujood bhi na thi phir aap ne ham ko sawar kara diya. ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki qism se ghaafil kar diya. qism Allah ki ham is harkat ke baad kabhi falaah nahi pa sakengey . to ham aap ki taraf lot kar aaey aur aap se ham ne uper wali tafseel ko arz kya ke ham aap ke paas aaey they taake aap ham ko sawari par Sawar kara dein to aap ne qism kha li thi ke aap ham ko sawar nahi karaaeingey aur dar-haqiqat us waqt aap ke paas sawari maujood bhi na thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sab sun kar farmaya ke maine tum ko sawar nahi karaya balke Allah ne tum ko sawar kara diya. Allah ki qism jab main koi qism kha leta hun baad mein us se behtar aur mamla dekhta hun to main wahi karta hun jo behtar hota hai aur us qism ka kaffara ada kar deta hun."
6650,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne qism khaaii aur kaha ke '' laat w uzzaa ki qism '' to usey phir kalima ( لا إله إلا الله ( keh lena chahiye aur jo shakhs apne sathi se kahey ke aao juwa khelein to usey chahiye ke (iske kaffara mein) sadqa kare.
6651,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki aik anguthi banwaai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey pahntey they, iska nageena hatheli ke hissey ki taraf rakhtey they. phir logon ne bhi aisi anguthiyan banwaa lein iske baad aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par baithey aur apni anguthi utaar di aur farmaya ke main usey pehnta tha aur iska nageena andar ki taraf rakhta tha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey utaar kar phenk diya aur farmaya ke Allah ki qism mein ab usey kabhi nahi pahnoonga. to logon ne bhi apni anguthiyan utaar kar phenk din."
6652,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo Islam ke siwa kisi aur mazhab par qism khaaey to wo aisa hi hai jaise ke usne qism khaaii hai aur jo shakhs apne nafs ko kisi cheez se halaak karey wo dozakh mein usi cheez se azab diya jata rahega aur momin par laanat bhejna usko qatl karne ke barabar hai aur jisne kisi momin par kufr ka ilzam lagaya to wo bhi uske qatl karne ke barabar hai.''
6653,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke Bani-Israeel mein teen shakhs they Allah ne unko aazmaanaa chaha ( phir Sara qissa bayan kya ( Farishtey ko kodhii ke paas bheja wo us se kehney laga meri rozii ke sarey zariey kat gaey hain ab Allah hi ka aasraa hai phir tera (ya ab Allah hi ki madad darkaar hai phir teri ( phir poori hadis ko zikr kya."
6654,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism khaney waley ko sachcha karne ka hukm farmaayaa.
6655,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ( Zenab ( ne aapko bula bheja us waqt aap ke paas Usama-bin-Zaid aur Sad-bin-Ubada aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi baithey they. sahibzadi saahiba ne kelha bheja ke unka bachcha marney ke qareeb hai aap tashrif laaiye. aap ne unke jawab mein yun kelha bheja mera salam kaho aur kaho sab Allah ka maal hai jo usney ley liya aur jo usney inayat farmaya aur har cheez ka uske paas waqt muqarrar hai, sabr karo aur Allah se sawab ki ummeed rakho . sahibzadi saahiba ne qism de kar phir kelha bheja ke nahi aap zaroor tashrif laaiye . us waqt aap uthey , ham log bhi sath uthey jab aap sahibzadi saahiba ke ghar par pahunchey aur wahan ja kar baithey to bachchey ko utha kar aap ke paas laey. aap ne usey god mein bitha liya wo dam tod raha tha. ye ranj bhara haal dekh kar aap ki aankhon se aansu bah nikley. Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye ronaa kaisa hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye ronaa raham ki wjah se hai aur Allah apne jis bandey ke dil mein chahta hai raham rakhta hai ya ye hai ke Allah apne un hi bandon par raham karega jo dusron par raham kartey hain."
6656,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis musalman ke teen bachchey mar jayen to usko dozakh ki aag nahi chhueygii magar sirf qism utaarney ke liye. ''
6657,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke main tum ko bataun jannati kon log hain, har aik ghareeb kamzor jo agar Allah ke bharosey par qism kha baithey to Allah usko sachcha karey ( uski qism poori kar de) aur dozakhi kon log hain har aik motaa, ladaakaa, maghroor aur fasaadii."
6658,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kon log achchhey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mera zamana , phir wo log jo us se qareeb hongey phir wo log jo us se qareeb hongey. iske baad aik aisi qaum paida hogi jiski gawahi qism se pahley zaban par aa jaya karegi aur qism gawahi se pahley . Ibrahim ne kaha ke hamarey asaatza jab ham kam Umr they, to hamein qism khaney se mana kya kartey they ke ham gawahi ya ahad mein qism khaaein ."
6659,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne jhooti qism is maqsad se khaaii ke kisi musalman ka maal iske zariey naajaaiz tareeqey par hasil karey to wo Allah Taala se is haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazab naak hoga. phir Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq nazil ki) Quran Majeed mein ke) ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله‏ ( bila shubah wo log jo Allah ke ahad ke zariey khareedtey hain.''
6660,"phir Ashas bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) wahan se guzrey aur puchha ke Abdullah tum se kya bayan kar rahe they. ham ne unse bayan kya to Ashas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye aayat mere aur mere aik sathi ke barey mein nazil hui thi, aik kuwein ke silsiley mein ham donon ka jhagdaa tha."
6661,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jahannam barabar yahi kehti rahegi ke kya kuchh aur hai kya kuchh aur hai? aakhir Allah tabarak w taala apna qadam usmein rakh dega to wo keh uthegi bas bas mein bhar gaee, teri izzat ki qasam! aur iska kuchh hissey kuchh ko khaney lagega.'' us riwayat ko Shoba ne Qatada se naql kya."
6662,"maine Urwa bin Zubair, Saeed-bin-Musaiyab, Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi siddiiqa (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat ke mutaalliq suna ke jab tohmat lagaaney waley ne un par tohmat lagai thi aur Allah Taala ne unko us se barii qarar diya tha aur har shakhs ne mujh se poori baat ka koi aik hissey hi bayan kaa. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai ke barey mein madad chaahi. phir Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Allah ki qasam! (لعمر الله) ham zaroor usey qatl kar dengey ( mufassal hadis peechhey guzar chuki hai)."
6663,aayat لا يؤاخذكم الله باللغو ''Allaah taala tum se laghw qasmon ke barey mein pakad nahi karega .'' rawi ne bayan kya ke Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye aayat لا ، Mina والله بلى والله‏ ( be-saakhta jo qismein aadat bana li jati hain) ke barey mein nazil hui thi.
6664,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Allah Taala ne meri ummat ki un ghaltiyon ko maaf kya hai jinka sirf dil mein waswasa guzrey ya dil mein uske karne ki khahish paida ho, magar iske mutabiq amal na ho aur na baat ki ho."
6665,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hijjatul-wadaa mein) qurbani ke din khutba de rahe they ke aik sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! main falan-falan arkaan ko falan-falan arkaan se pahley khayal karta tha (is ghalati se unko aagey peechhey ada kya ( iske baad doosrey sahib khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main falan-falan arkaan Haj ke mutaalliq yoonhii khayal karta tha unka ishara (halaq, rami aur nahar) ki taraf tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yoonhii kar lo (taqdeem w taakheer karne mein) aaj unmein se kisi kaam mein koi harj nahi hai. chunanche us din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jis mas'ale mein bhi puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ke kar lo koi harj nahi."
6666,"aik sahabi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha, maine rami karne se pahley tawaaf ziyaarat kar liya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi harj nahi. teesrey ne kaha ke maine rami karne se pahley hi zabah kar liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi harj nahi."
6667,"aik sahabi masjide-Nabawi mein Namaz padhney ke liye aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid ke aik kinarey tashrif rakhtey they. phir wo sahabi aaey aur salam kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ja phir Namaz padh , isliye ke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. wo wapas gaey aur phir Namaz padh kar aaey aur salam kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi unse yahi farmaya ke wapas ja aur Namaz padh kyonke tu ney Namaz nahi padhi. aakhir teesri martaba mein wo sahabi boley ke phir mujhey Namaz ka tariqa sikhaa dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum Namaz ke liye khadey hua karo to pahley poori tarah wuzu kar liya karo, phir qible ki taraf rukh karkey takbeer kaho aur jo kuchh Quran Majeed main tumhen yad hai aur tum aasani ke sath padh saktey ho usey padha karo, phir rukoo karo aur sukoon ke sath rukoo kar chuko to apna sar uthao aur jab seedhey khadey ho jao to sajda karo, jab sajdey ki haalat main achi tarah ho jao to sajde se sar uthaao, yahan tak ke seedhey ho jao aur itminan se baith jao, phir sajda karo aur jab itminan se sajda kar lo to sar uthao yahan tak ke seedhey khadey ho jao, ye amal tum apni poori Namaz mein karo."
6668,"jab Uhud ki ladai mein mushrik shikast kha gaey aur apni shikast unmein mashhoor ho gaee to iblees ne cheekh kar kaha ( musalmanon se) ke aey Allah ke bando! peechhey dushman hai chunanche aagey ke log peechhey ki taraf pil padey aur peechhey waley (musalmanon hi se) lad padey. is haalat mein Huzaifa-bin-Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke log unke musalman walid ko be-khabri mein mar rahe hain to unhon-ne musalmanon se kaha ke ye to mere walid hain jo musalman hain, mere walid ! Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism log phir bhi baaz nahi aaey aur aakhir unhein qatl kar hi dala. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Allah tumhari maghfirat kare. Urwa ne bayan kya ke Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne walid ki is tarah shahadat ka aakhir waqt tak ranj aur afsos hi raha yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja miley."
6669,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne roza rakha ho aur bhool kar kha liya ho to usey apna roza pura kar lena chahiye kyonke usey Allah ne khilaaya pilaya hai.''
6670,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhai aur pehli 2 rakaat ke baad baithney se pahley hi uth gaey aur Namaz poori kar li. jab Namaz padh chukey to logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke salam ka intizar kya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer kahi aur salam pherney se pahley sajda kya, phir sajde se sar uthaya aur dobara takbeer keh kar sajda kya. phir sajde se sar uthaya aur salam phera ."
6671,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Zohar ki Namaz padhai aur Namaz mein koi cheez zyada ya kam kar di. Mansoor ne bayan kya ke mujhey malum nahi Ibrahim ko shuba hua tha ya Alqama ko. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke ya Rasulullah! Namaz mein kuchh kami kar di gaee hai ya aap bhool gaey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kya baat hai? logon ne kaha ke aap ne is-is tarah Namaz padhai hai. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath 2 sajdey (saho ke) kiye aur farmaya ye 2 sajdey us shakhs ke liye hain jisey yaqin na ho ke usne apni Namaz mein kami ya zyada kar di hai usey chahiye ke sahi baat tak pahunchne ke liye zahan par zor daley aur jo baqi reh gaya ho usey pura karey phir 2 sajdey ( saho ke) kar ley."
6672,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aayat لا تؤاخذني بما نسيت wla ترهقني من أمري عسرا‏ ke mutaalliq ke pehli martaba aetraz Musa (Alaihissalam) se bhool kar hua tha."
6673,"unke yahan kuchh unke mehman thahrey huey they, to unhon-ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke unke wapas aaney se pahley janwar zabah kar lein taake unke mehman khaaein, chunanche unhon-ne Namaz eidul-Azha se pahley janwar zabah kar liya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke Namaz ke baad dobara zabah karein. Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! mere paas aik saal se zyada doodh wali bakri hai jo 2 bakriyon ke gosht se badh kar hai. ibne- Auf Shabi ki hadis ke us maqam par thahar jatey they aur Muhammad-bin Sirin se usi hadis ki tarah hadis bayan kartey they aur us maqam par ruk kar kehtey they ke mujhey malum nahi, ye rukhsat doosrey logon ke liye bhi hai ya sirf Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye hi thi. uski riwayat Ayub ne Ibne-Sirin se ki hai, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
6674,main us waqt tak maujood tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eid ki Namaz padhai phir khutba diya aur farmaya ke jisne Namaz se pahley zabah kar liya ho usey chahiye ke uski jagah doosra janwar zabah karey aur jisne abhi zabah na kya ho usey chahiye ke Allah ka naam lekar janwar zabah kare.
6675,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kabeera gunah Allah ke sath shirk karnaa, waalidain ki nafarmani karnaa, kisi ki nahaq jaan lena aur) يمين الغموس‏) qasdan jhooti qism khaney ko kehtey hain."
6676,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne jhooti qism is taur se khaaii ke iske zariey kisi musalman ka maal naajaaiz tareeqe se hasil karey to wo Allah Taala se is haal mein milega ke Allah is par bahut hi ghussa hoga.'' phir Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq wahi ke zariey nazil ki) إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا‏ (ke '' bila shubah wo log jo Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ke badley maamooli duniya ki poonjii khareedtey hain'' aakhir aayat tak.
6677,"Abdullah ye hadis bayan kar chukey they, itney mein Ashas bin Qais aaey aur puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ne tum logon se kya hadis bayan ki hai? logon ne kaha is-is mazmoon ki. unhon-ne kaha ajii ye aayat to mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi mere aik chacha-zad bhai ki zameen mein mera aik kunwaan tha iske jhagdey ke silsile mein main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne gawah lao warna muddua-alaih se qism li jaeygi. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! phir wo to jhooti qism kha lega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne jhooti qism bd-niyati ke sath isliye khaaii ke iske zariey kisi musalman ka maal hadap kar jaey to qiyamat ke din Allah se is haal mein milega ke wo Allah is par intihai ghazabnaak hoga."
6678,mere sathiyon ne mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sawari ke janwar maangney ke liye bheja to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism main tumharey liye koi sawari ka janwar nahi de sakta (kyonke maujood nahi hain) jab main aap ke samney aaya to aap kuchh narazgi mein they. phir jab dobara aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne sathiyon ke paas ja aur keh ke Allah Taala ne ya (ye kaha ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumharey liye sawari ka intizam kar diya.
6679,"maine Urwa-bin-Zubair , Saeed bin Musaiyab , Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par bohtan ki baat ke mutaalliq , jab un par tohmat lagaaney walon ne tohmat lagai thi aur Allah Taala ne unko us tohmat se barii qarar diya tha, un sab logon ne mujh se us qissa ka koi aik tukda bayan kya (is hadis mein ye bhi hai ke) phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك‏ (ke '' bila shubah jin logon ne jhooti tohmat lagai hai'' das aayaton tak. jo sab ki sab meri paakii bayan karne ke liye nazil hui thin Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) , mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath qaraabat ki wjah se unka kharch apne zimme liye huey they, kaha ke Allah ki qism ab kabhi mistah par koi cheez aik paisa kharch nahi karunga. iske baad ke usne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par is tarah ki jhooti tohmat lagai hai. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) wla يأتل أولو al-Fazal منكم والسعة أن يؤتوا أولي القربى‏ ( الخ Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha, kyon nahi, Allah ki qism main to yahi pasand karta hun ke Allah meri maghfirat kar de. chunanche unhon-ne phir mistah ko wo kharch dena shuru kar diya jo us se pahley unhein diya kartey they aur kaha ke Allah ki qism mein ab kharch dene ko kabhi nahi rokoonga."
6680,"mein qabila ash'ar ke chand sathiyon ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jab main aap ke paas aaya to aap ghussa they phir ham ne aap se sawari ka janwar maanga to aap ne qism kha li ke aap hamarey liye iska intizam nahi kar saktey. iske baad farmaya : Allah ki qism , Allah ne chaha to main kabhi bhi agar koi qism kha loonga aur uske siwa dusri cheez mein bhalai dekhoonga to wahi karunga jis mein bhalai hogi aur qism tod doonga."
6681,jab janab abu-Taalib ki maut ka waqt qareeb hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas aaey aur kaha ke aap keh dijiye ke '' la ilaaha-illallaah '' to main aap ke liye Allah se jhagad sakunga .
6682,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' 2 kalimey jo zaban par halkey hain lekin taraazu par) aakhirat mein) bhari hain aur Allah Rehman ke yahan pasandida hain wo ye hain سبحان الله وبحمده ، Mina سبحان الله العظيم‏ .
6683,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aur maine (isii par guman kartey huey) doosra kalima kaha (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) jo shakhs is haal mein mar jaeyga ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thahraataa hoga to wo jahannam mein jaaeyga.'' aur maine dusri baat kahi ke jo shakhs is haal mein mar jaeyga ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraataa hoga wo jannat mein jaeyga
6684,"aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon mein moch aa gaee thi. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne bula khaane mein untees din tak thahre huey rahe phir wahan se utrey, logon ne kaha ya Rasulullah! aap ne iilaa aik mahiney ke liye kya tha? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye mahina untees din ka hai."
6685,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne nikah kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni shadi ke mauqe par bulaya. dulhan hi unki mezbaanii ka kaam kar rahi thin, phir Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon se poochha, tumhen malum hai, maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kya pilaya tha. kaha ke raat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye maine khajoor aik badey piyaale mein bhigo di thi aur subah ke waqt uska pani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pilaya tha."
6686,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi saahiba Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke unki aik bakri mar gaee to uske chamdey ko ham ne dabaaghat de diya. phir ham uski mashk mein nabeez banatey rahe yahan tak ke wo puraanii ho gaee.
6687,"aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi pai-dar-pai teen din tak saalan ke sath gehun ki roti nahi kha sakey yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja miley aur ibne-kaseer ne bayan kya ke ham ko Sufiyan ne khabar di ke ham se Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya, unse unke walid ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
6688,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apni biwi ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke main sun kar aa raha hun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz (faaqon ki wjah se) kamzor pad gaee hai aur maine awaz se aap ke faaqe ka andaza lagaya hai. kya tumharey paas khaney ki koi cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha haan. chunanche unhon-ne jau ki chand rotiyaan nikaaliin aur aik odhnii lekar roti ko uske aik koney se lapet diya aur usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhijwaayaa . main lekar gaya to maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif rakhtey hain aur aap ke sath kuchh log hain, main unke paas ja ke khada ho gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha, kya tumhen abu-Talha ne bheja hai, maine arz kya : ji haan. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un logon se kaha jo sath they ke utho aur chalo, main unke aagey-aagey chal raha tha. aakhir mein abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan pahuncha aur unko itlaa di. abu-Talha ne kaha : Umme-Sulaim! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey hain aur hamarey paas to koi aisa khana nahi hai jo sab ko pesh kya ja sakey? unhon-ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bahar nikley aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley, iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur abu-Talha ghar ki taraf badhey aur andar gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Umme-Sulaim! jo kuchh tumharey paas hai mere paas laao. wo yahi rotiyaan laaein. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se un rotiyon ko chooraa kar diya gaya aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni aik ( ghi ki) kapii ko nichodaa gaya yahi saalan tha. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jaisa ke Allah ne chaha dua padhi aur farmaya ke das das aadmiyon ko andar bulao unhein bulaya gaya aur is tarah sab logon ne khaya aur khub sair ho gaey, haaziriin ki tadaad 70 ya usi aadmiyon ki thi."
6689,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke bila shubah amal ka daro-madar niyat par hai aur insan ko wahi milega jiski wo niyat karega to jiski hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ke liye hogi to waqei wo unhiin ke liye hogi aur jiski hijrat duniya hasil karne ke liye ya kisi aurat se shadi karne ke liye hogi to uski hijrat usi ke liye hogi jiske liye us ne hijrat ki.
6690,"jab Kab (Raziallahu anhu) naa-beenaa ho gaey they, to unki aulad mein aik yahi kahin aaney janey mein unke sath rahtey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se unke waaqie aur aayat على الثلاثة الذين خلفوا ke silsile mein suna, unhon-ne apni hadis ke aakhir mein kaha ke (maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ye pesh kash! ki ke) apni tauba ki khushi mein main apna maal Allah aur uske rasool ke Deen ki khidmat mein sadqa kar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke apna kuchh maal apne paas hi rakho, ye tumharey liye behtar hai."
6691,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ummul-momeneen) Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan rukte they aur shehad peetey they. phir maine aur (ummul-momeneen) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne ahad kya ke ham mein se jiske paas bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaein to wo kahey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh se maghaafeer ki bu aati hai, aap ne maghaafeer to nahi khaaii hai? chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab aik ke yahan tashrif laey to unhon-ne yahi baat aap se poochhii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke maine shehad piyaa hai Zenab binte-Jahash ke yahan aur ab kabhi nahi piyunga. (kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yaqin ho gaya ke waqei usmein maghaafeer ki bu aati hai) is par ye aayat nazil hui (ya أيها النبي لم تحرم ما أحل الله لك ( ''aey Nabi ! aap aisi cheez kyon haram kartey hain jo Allah ne aap ke liye halal ki hai.'' ( إن تتوبا إلى الله ( main Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf ishara hai aur وإذ أسر النبي إلى بعض أزواجه حديثا se ishara Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ki taraf hai ke '' nahi '' maine shehad piyaa hai.'' aur mujh se Ibrahim bin-Musa ne Hisham se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ab kabhi mein shehad nahi piyunga maine qism kha li hai tum uski kisi ko khabar na karna (phir aap ne us qism ko tod diyaa) ."
6692,"unhon-ne kaha, kya logon ko nazar se mana nahi kya gaya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nazar kisi cheez ko na aagey kar sakti hai na peechhey , albatta iske zariey kanjoos ka maal nikala ja sakta hai."
6693,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar se mana farmaya tha aur farmaya tha ke wo kisi cheez ko wapas nahi kar saktii, albatta iske zariey kanjoos ka maal nikala ja sakta hai."
6694,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' nazar insan ko koi aisi cheez nahi deti jo iske muqaddar mein na ho, albatta Allah Taala iske zariey kanjoos se uska maal nikalwaataa hai aur is tarah wo cheezein sadqa kar deta hai jiski us se pahley uski ummeed nahi ki ja sakti thii.''"
6695,"maine Imran-bin-Husain se suna, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein sabse behtar mera zamana hai, iske baad unka jo iske qareeb hongey. iske baad wo jo us se qareeb hongey.'' Imran ne bayan kya ke mujhey yad nahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne zamane ke baad 2 ka zikr kya tha ya teen ka ( farmaya ke) phir aik aisi qaum aaeygii jo nazar maanegii aur usey pura nahi karegi , khayanat karegi aur un par aitimad nahi rahega. wo gawahi dene ke liye taiyaar rahengey jabke unse gawahi ke liye kaha bhi nahi jaeyga aur unmein mutaapaa aam ho jaeyga"
6696,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne iski nazar maana ho ke Allah ki itaat karega to usey itaat karni chahiye lekin jisne Allah ki gunah (naafarmaanii) ki nazar maana ho usey na karni chaahiye.''
6697,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke masjide-Haraam mein aik raat ka aetikaf karunga ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni nazar poori kar.
6698,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik nazar ke barey mein puchha jo unki walida ke zimma baqi thi aur unki maut nazar poori karne se pahley ho gaee thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein fatwa diya ke nazar wo apni maa ki taraf se poori kar dein. chunanche baad mein yahi tariqa masnoona qarar paya.
6699,aik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur arz kya ke meri behan ne nazar maana thi ke Haj karengii lekin ab unka intiqal ho chuka hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar un par koi qarz hota to kya tum usey ada kartey ? unhon-ne kaha zaroor ada kartey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Allah ka qarz bhi ada karo kyonke wo iska zyada mustahiq hai ke iska qarz pura ada kya jaey.
6700,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne Allah ki itaat ki nazar maana ho usey chahiye ke itaat karey aur jisne gunah karne ki nazar maana ho to wo gunah na kare. ''
6701,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala us se be-parwaa hai ke ye shakhs apni jaan ko azab mein daaley.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey dekha ke wo apne 2 beton ke darmyan chal raha tha aur fazari ne bayan kya, unse Humaid ne, unse Sabit ne bayan kya aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
6702,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha ke wo Kaba ka tawaaf lagaam ya iske siwa kisi aur cheez ke zariey kar raha tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kaat diya.
6703,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guzrey to Kaba ka aik shakhs is tarah tawaaf kar raha tha ke doosra shakhs uski naak mein rassii baandh kar uske aagey se uski rehnumai kar raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo rassii apne hath se kaat di, phir hukm diya ke hath se uski rehnumai kare."
6704,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they ke aik shakhs ko khadey dekha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske mutaalliq puchha to logon ne bataya ke ye abu-Israaeel naam ke hain. unhon-ne nazar maana hai ke khadey hi rahengey, baithengey nahi, na kisi cheez ke saaye mein baithengey aur na kisi se baat karengey aur roza rakhengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unse kaho ke baat karein, saaye ke nichey baithein uthein aur apna roza pura kar lein. abdul-wahaab ne bayan kya ke ham se Ayub ne bayan kya, unse Ikrima ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
6705,unse aisey shakhs ke mutaalliq puchha gaya jisne nazar maana ho ke kuchh makhsoos dinon mein rozey rakhega . phir ittifaq se unhiin dinon mein Baaqar eid ya eid ke din pad gaey hon? Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baaqar eid aur eid ke din rozey nahi rakhtey they aur na un dinon mein rozey ko jaaiz samajhtey they.
6706,mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha aik shakhs ne unse puchha ke maine nazar maana hai ke har mangal ya buddh ke din roza rakhoonga. ittifaq se isi din ki Baaqar eid pad gaee hai? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne nazar poori karne ka hukm diya hai aur hamein Baaqar eid ke din roza rakhney ki manaahii ki gaee hai. us shakhs ne dobara apna sawal dohraya to aap ne phir us se sirf itni hi baat kahi is par koi zyadti nahi ki.
6707,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar ki ladai ke liye nikley. us ladai mein hamein sona , chandi ghaneemat mein nahi mila tha balke doosrey amwaal , kapdey aur saman mila tha. phir bani Khubaib ke aik shakhs Rifaa bin Zaid naam ke ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik ghulam hadiye mein diya ghulam ka naam mud'am tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi Quraa ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur jab aap wadi ul-Quraa mein pahunch gaey to mud'am ko jabke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kajaawa durust kar raha tha. aik anjaan teer aa kar laga aur uski maut ho gaee. logon ne kaha ke jannat usey Mubarak ho, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai wo kambal jo usney taqseem se pahley khaibar ke maale-ghanimat mein se churaa liya tha, wo is par aag ka angaara bin kar bhid raha hai. jab logon ne ye baat suni to aik shakhs chappal ka tasma ya 2 tasmey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aag ka tasma hai ya 2 tasmey aag ke hain."
